# Supabase Configuration
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here

# StealthGPT for content humanization (optional - browser-side)
VITE_STEALTHGPT_API_KEY=your-stealthgpt-key-here

# Notes:
# 1. Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your actual values
# 2. Never commit .env.local to version control
# 3. Get Supabase credentials from: https://app.supabase.com
# 4. AI API keys (Claude, Grok, DataForSEO) are configured as
#    Supabase Edge Function secrets, NOT browser env vars.
#    Set them via: supabase secrets set CLAUDE_API_KEY=xxx
